ffer injuries to its feet and legs that slow its speed by one-third. This movement penalty lasts for 24 hours or until the injured creature receives a cure spell (which also restores lost hit points). Another character can remove the penalty by taking 10 
minutes to dress the injuries and succeeding at a Heal check against the spell\rquote s save DC.
